@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vbmhyr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.58 - v0 + 0.24) - (v2 + 0.52 * v0 + 0.93)) / v1)
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.23 + tmp + 0.44) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.13)) - wp.exp((tmp + 0.37 + v0 + 0.66)))
    v1 = (v1 / wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.27)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    v0 = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
